() Tj
T*
(The threshold is not a learned probability boundary. It is an operational cutoff for a) Tj
T*
(review-first workflow where false positives and false negatives are treated as roughly) Tj
T*
(comparable. In this run, the heuristic-only flag rate was 0.72%, while the ML upper-tail) Tj
T*
(reference rate was 1.50%; those rates are reported separately so reviewers can see how) Tj
T*
